  "detailed_description": "A game about squares and patterns.<br><br>In ²Pattern, you have to <strong>move and swap pieces</strong> on one side and the other to <strong>reproduce a minimalist pattern.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/fb3e12aa9fa34a406d51667fec71670e.poster.avif?t=1738523293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/fb3e12aa9fa34a406d51667fec71670e.webm?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/fb3e12aa9fa34a406d51667fec71670e.mp4?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are 50+ patterns to be reproduced. You can play at your own pace and enjoy the game atmosphere.<br>You can still challenge yourself by enabling a timer before starting if you want to!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/9bf485e294de8f0b589e6081bacd2cbb.poster.avif?t=1738523293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/9bf485e294de8f0b589e6081bacd2cbb.webm?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/9bf485e294de8f0b589e6081bacd2cbb.mp4?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Headphones are highly recommended!</i>",
  "about_the_game": "A game about squares and patterns.<br><br>In ²Pattern, you have to <strong>move and swap pieces</strong> on one side and the other to <strong>reproduce a minimalist pattern.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/fb3e12aa9fa34a406d51667fec71670e.poster.avif?t=1738523293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/fb3e12aa9fa34a406d51667fec71670e.webm?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/fb3e12aa9fa34a406d51667fec71670e.mp4?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are 50+ patterns to be reproduced. You can play at your own pace and enjoy the game atmosphere.<br>You can still challenge yourself by enabling a timer before starting if you want to!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/9bf485e294de8f0b589e6081bacd2cbb.poster.avif?t=1738523293\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/9bf485e294de8f0b589e6081bacd2cbb.webm?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164040/extras/9bf485e294de8f0b589e6081bacd2cbb.mp4?t=1738523293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Headphones are highly recommended!</i>",
